subject: Figure Skating
Olympic Games (2010)
United States Figure Skating Championships
Awards, Decorations and Honors
lead_paragraph: Caydee Denney and Jeremy Barrett won their first national championship in dominating fashion, becoming one of the two American pairs teams headed to the Vancouver Games.
